#: filters/native-filter.cc:182
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This file was created by Kig version \"%1\".\n"
"Support for older Kig formats (pre-0.4) has been removed from Kig.\n"
"You can try to open this file with an older Kig version (0.4 to 0.6),\n"
"and then save it again, which will save it in the new format."
msgstr ""
"ໄຟລ໌ນີ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍ Kig ເວີຊັນ \"%1\".\n"
"ການຮອງຮັບຮູບແບບ Kig ເກົ່າ (ກ່ອນ 0.4) ໄດ້ຖືກນຳອອກຈາກ Kig ແລ້ວ.\n"
"ທ່ານສາມາດລອງເປີດໄຟລ໌ນີ້ດ້ວຍ Kig ເວີຊັນເກົ່າ (0.4 ຫາ 0.6),\n"
"ແລະ ບັນທຶກມັນອີກຄັ້ງ, ເຊິ່ງຈະບັນທຶກໃນຮູບແບບໃໝ່."

#: filters/native-filter.cc:212 filters/native-filter.cc:391
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This Kig file has a coordinate system that this Kig version does not "
"support.\n"
"A standard coordinate system will be used instead."
msgstr ""
"ໄຟລ໌ Kig ນີ້ມີລະບົບພິກັດທີ່ Kig ເວີຊັນນີ້ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບ.\n"
"ຈະໃຊ້ລະບົບພິກັດມາດຕະຖານແທນ."

#: filters/native-filter.cc:305 filters/native-filter.cc:487
#: objects/object_imp_factory.cc:435
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This Kig file uses an object of type \"%1\", which this Kig version does not "
"support.Perhaps you have compiled Kig without support for this object type,"
"or perhaps you are using an older Kig version."
msgstr ""
"ໄຟລ໌ Kig ນີ້ໃຊ້ວັດຖຸປະເພດ \"%1\", ເຊິ່ງ Kig ເວີຊັນນີ້ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບ. ບາງທີທ່ານອາດຈະຄອມໄພລ໌ Kig "
"ໂດຍບໍ່ມີການຮອງຮັບປະເພດວັດຖຸນີ້, ຫຼື ບາງທີທ່ານອາດຈະກຳລັງໃຊ້ Kig ເວີຊັນເກົ່າຢູ່."

#: filters/native-filter.cc:358
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This Kig file uses an object of type \"%1\", which is obsolete, you should "
"save the construction with a different name and check that it works as "
"expected."
msgstr ""
"ໄຟລ໌ Kig ນີ້ໃຊ້ວັດຖຸປະເພດ \"%1\", ເຊິ່ງລ້າສະໄໝແລ້ວ, ທ່ານຄວນບັນທຶກການສ້າງດ້ວຍຊື່ໃໝ່ ແລະ "
"ກວດເບິ່ງວ່າມັນເຮັດວຽກຕາມທີ່ຄາດໄວ້ຫຼືບໍ່."

