#: kig/aboutdata.h:25
#, kde-format
msgid "Dominique Devriese"
msgstr "Dominique Devriese"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:25
#, kde-format
msgid "Original author, former maintainer, design and lots of code."
msgstr "ຜູ້ຂຽນຕົ້ນສະບັບ, ອະດີດຜູ້ບຳລຸງຮັກສາ, ອອກແບບ ແລະ ຂຽນໂຄ້ດຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:27
#, kde-format
msgid "Maurizio Paolini"
msgstr "Maurizio Paolini"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:28
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Did a lot of important work all around Kig, including, but not limited to "
"conics, cubics, transformations and property tests support."
msgstr ""
"ໄດ້ເຮັດວຽກສຳຄັນຫຼາຍຢ່າງໃນ Kig, ລວມທັງແຕ່ບໍ່ຈຳກັດພຽງພາກຕັດຈວຍ, ຄິວບິກ, ການແປງ ແລະ "
"ການຮອງຮັບການທົດສອບຄຸນສົມບັດ."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:33
#, kde-format
msgid "Pino Toscano"
msgstr "Pino Toscano"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:34
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Former maintainer, Dr. Geo import filter, point and line styles, Italian "
"translation, miscellaneous stuff here and there."
msgstr ""
"ອະດີດຜູ້ບຳລຸງຮັກສາ, ຕົວຄັດຕອງການນຳເຂົ້າ Dr. Geo, ຮູບແບບຈຸດ ແລະ ເສັ້ນ, ການແປພາສາອິຕາລີ, ແລະ "
"ສິ່ງອື່ນໆທົ່ວໄປ."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:39
#, kde-format
msgid "Franco Pasquarelli"
msgstr "Franco Pasquarelli"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:40
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Helped a lot with the implementation of the Locus object, there's quite some "
"math involved in doing it right, and Franco wrote the most difficult parts."
msgstr ""
"ຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຢ່າງຫຼາຍໃນການປະຕິບັດວັດຖຸ Locus, ມີຄະນິດສາດຂ້ອນຂ້າງຫຼາຍໃນການເຮັດໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ, ແລະ "
"Franco ໄດ້ຂຽນສ່ວນທີ່ຍາກທີ່ສຸດ."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:45
#, kde-format
msgid "Francesca Gatti"
msgstr "Francesca Gatti"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:46
#, kde-format
msgid "Responsible for the computation of the algebraic equation of a locus."
msgstr "ຮັບຜິດຊອບໃນການຄິດໄລ່ສົມຜົນພຶດຊະຄະນິດຂອງ Locus."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:50
#, kde-format
msgid "Petr Gajdos"
msgstr "Petr Gajdos"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:50
#, kde-format
msgid "Contributed the Bézier curves and related icons."
msgstr "ປະກອບສ່ວນເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງ Bézier ແລະ ໄອຄອນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:52
#, kde-format
msgid "Raoul Bourquin"
msgstr "Raoul Bourquin"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:52
#, kde-format
msgid "Contributed the 'asymptote' export filter."
msgstr "ປະກອບສ່ວນຕົວຄັດຕອງການສົ່ງອອກ 'asymptote'."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:54
#, kde-format
msgid "Eric Depagne"
msgstr "Eric Depagne"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:55
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The French translator, who also contributed some useful feedback, like "
"feature requests and bug reports."
