"ນັກແປພາສາຝຣັ່ງ, ຜູ້ທີ່ຍັງປະກອບສ່ວນຄຳຕິຊົມທີ່ເປັນປະໂຫຍດ, ເຊັ່ນ: ການຮ້ອງຂໍຄຸນສົມບັດ ແລະ "
"ລາຍງານຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:59
#, kde-format
msgid "Marc Bartsch"
msgstr "Marc Bartsch"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:60
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Author of KGeo, where I got inspiration, some source, and most of the "
"artwork from."
msgstr "ຜູ້ຂຽນ KGeo, ບ່ອນທີ່ຂ້ອຍໄດ້ຮັບແຮງບັນດານໃຈ, ບາງຊອດໂຄ້ດ, ແລະ ວຽກສິນລະປະສ່ວນໃຫຍ່."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:64
#, kde-format
msgid "Christophe Devriese"
msgstr "Christophe Devriese"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:65
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Domi's brother, who he got to write the algorithm for calculating the center "
"of the circle with three points given."
msgstr "ອ້າຍຂອງ Domi, ຜູ້ທີ່ຂຽນອັນກໍຣິດຶມສຳລັບການຄິດໄລ່ຈຸດໃຈກາງຂອງວົງມົນດ້ວຍສາມຈຸດທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:70
#, kde-format
msgid "Christophe Prud'homme"
msgstr "Christophe Prud'homme"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:70
#, kde-format
msgid "Contributed a patch for some bugs."
msgstr "ປະກອບສ່ວນແພັດຊ໌ສຳລັບບາງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#: kig/aboutdata.h:72
#, kde-format
msgid "Robert Gogolok"
msgstr "Robert Gogolok"

#: kig/aboutdata.h:73
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Contributed some good feedback on Kig, some feature requests, cleanups and "
