#: objects/transform_types.cc:583
msgid "Select the fourth of the four end points of the generic projectivity..."
msgstr "ເລືອກຈຸດທີສີ່ຂອງສີ່ຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດຂອງໂປຣເຈັກຕິວິຕີທົ່ວໄປ..."

#: objects/transform_types.cc:624
