"Select the argument objects (if any)\n"
"in the Kig window and press \"Next\"."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກວັດຖຸອາກິວເມັນ (ຖ້າມີ)\n"
"ໃນໜ້າຕ່າງ Kig ແລ້ວກົດ \"ຕໍ່ໄປ\"."

#: scripting/newscriptwizard.cc:62
#, kde-format
